== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Sketcher_ArcOverlay.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_ArcOverlay|Sketcher ArcOverlay]] tool shows or hides the circular helpers (underlying virtual circles) for arcs in all sketches. When shown, they help recognize where constraints apply to arcs.
</div>

